 text-black dark:text-white\",\"children\":\"Technical Specifications\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm lg:text-base font-normal leading-relaxed max-inline-size-prose text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-4\",\"children\":\"Accessibility of isaacavazquez.com relies on the following technologies:\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"HTML5\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"CSS3\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"JavaScript (React/Next.js)\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"ARIA (Accessible Rich Internet Applications)\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"lg:text-base font-normal mb-4 max-inline-size-prose text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 mt-4 text-sm\",\"children\":\"These technologies are relied upon for conformance with the accessibility standards used.\"}]]}]\nc:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-primary)] p-6 sm:p-8\",\"role\":\"article\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight mb-4 text-black dark:text-white\",\"children\":\"Assessment Approach\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm lg:text-base font-normal leading-relaxed max-inline-size-prose text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-4\",\"children\":\"I assessed the accessibility of isaacavazquez.com by the following approaches:\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Self-evaluation and code review\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Manual keyboard navigation testing\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Contrast ratio analysis (21:1 for primary text)\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Touch target measurement (44px minimum)\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Reduced motion preference testing\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Semantic HTML validation\"}]]}]]}]\nd:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-primary)] p-6 sm:p-8\",\"role\":\"article\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight mb-4 text-black dark:text-white\",\"children\":\"Known Limitations\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm lg:text-base font-normal leading-relaxed max-inline-size-prose text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 mb-4\",\"children\":\"Despite my best efforts to ensure accessibility, some areas for improvement remain. I am actively working to:\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Complete comprehensive screen reader testing with multiple assistive technologies\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Achieve AAA contrast (7:1) for all text elements (currently: primary and secondary meet AAA, tertiary meets AA)\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Expand public-facing keyboard shortcut documentation\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm lg:text-base font-normal leading-relaxed mb-4 max-inline-size-prose text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 mt-4\",\"children\":\"If you encounter any accessibility barriers, please contact me so I can address them promptly.\"}]]}]\ne:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"lg:text-base font-normal mb-4 max-inline-size-prose text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-500 text-center\",\"children\":[\"This accessibility statement was created on November 2025 and reflects our ongoing commitment to digital accessibility. For more information about web accessibility, visit the\",\" \",[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"https://www.w3.org/WAI/\",\"